===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''gadfly''' (''plural:'' '''[[gadflies]]''')
# Any [[dipterous]] [[insect]] of the [[genus]] Oestrus, and allied group of [[botfly|botflies]].
# A [[fly]] of various species, of the family Tabanid[ae], noted for [[buzz]]ing about animals and [[suck]]ing their blood.
# A [[horsefly]].
# (''slang'') A bloodsucker
#: ''He's a regular '''gadfly''' and takes advantage of his friend's generosity.''

